  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink52-kilavi">vāyil peṟṟuk kūṭiyirunta talaimakaṟkut tōḻi nakaiyāṭic colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink52">
          <l>vayalaic ceṅkoṭip piṇaiya ṟaiic</l>
          <l>cevviral civanta cēyari maḻaikkaṭ</l>
          <l>cevvāyk kuṟumaka ḷiṉaiya</l>
          <l>vevvāy muṉṉiṉṟu makiḻnaniṉ ṟērē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">


          <l> While a little woman with a red mouth despairs, </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> her raining eyes streaked with red </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> her fingers stained red </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> from stringing a wreath of red purslane creepers–</l>
          <l> Which place, o delightful man, did your chariot stop before (this)? </l>
          <l> OR: before which place, o delightful man, has your chariot been standing? </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
